'''WRCO-FM''' (100.9 [[FM broadcasting|FM]], "Country & Community") is a [[radio station]] broadcasting a [[country music]] format.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.arbitron.com |date=Winter 2010 |title=Station Information Profile |publisher=[[Arbitron]] |accessdate=2010-03-07}}</ref> Licensed to [[Richland Center, Wisconsin]], USA, the station is currently owned by Fruit Broadcasting, LLC and features programing from [[CBS Radio]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fcc.gov/fcc-bin/fmq?call=WRCO-FM |title=WRCO-FM Facility Record |work=United States [[Federal Communications Commission]], audio division |accessdate=2010-03-07}}</ref>
